  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You woke up early to reach the Hōkan-ji temple before any other tourists, yet you don't seem to be getting any closer. You've become trapped in an endless loop, and the only way out is to spot what doesn’t belong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9bb7f4768fa9928b1547ee1c6c52d628.poster.avif?t=1773561199\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9bb7f4768fa9928b1547ee1c6c52d628.webm?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9bb7f4768fa9928b1547ee1c6c52d628.mp4?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kyoto Anomaly takes between 30 and 90 minutes to complete, with multiple endings.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay close attention to your surroundings. Notice anything wrong? Head left. Everything in order? Go right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/c482e020de77ab3442730043ac7764a1.poster.avif?t=1773561199\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/c482e020de77ab3442730043ac7764a1.webm?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/c482e020de77ab3442730043ac7764a1.mp4?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your path carefully, or be lost forever...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 32 unique anomalies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice-acted (Japanese / English)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can pet the cat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9de95657629cd0d678cae6a576080fdb.poster.avif?t=1773561199\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9de95657629cd0d678cae6a576080fdb.webm?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9de95657629cd0d678cae6a576080fdb.mp4?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You woke up early to reach the Hōkan-ji temple before any other tourists, yet you don't seem to be getting any closer. You've become trapped in an endless loop, and the only way out is to spot what doesn’t belong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9bb7f4768fa9928b1547ee1c6c52d628.poster.avif?t=1773561199\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9bb7f4768fa9928b1547ee1c6c52d628.webm?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9bb7f4768fa9928b1547ee1c6c52d628.mp4?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kyoto Anomaly takes between 30 and 90 minutes to complete, with multiple endings.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay close attention to your surroundings. Notice anything wrong? Head left. Everything in order? Go right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/c482e020de77ab3442730043ac7764a1.poster.avif?t=1773561199\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/c482e020de77ab3442730043ac7764a1.webm?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/c482e020de77ab3442730043ac7764a1.mp4?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your path carefully, or be lost forever...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 32 unique anomalies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice-acted (Japanese / English)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can pet the cat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9de95657629cd0d678cae6a576080fdb.poster.avif?t=1773561199\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9de95657629cd0d678cae6a576080fdb.webm?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3631850/extras/9de95657629cd0d678cae6a576080fdb.mp4?t=1773561199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
